{"tid":573262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實肥絲錯系邊度？系你老母啦。","createTime":"2018-02-26T10:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T11:15:54.000Z","uid":36334,"like":36,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b516658885c79b232c1a137341f2022646e83216","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"系你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打個「系」字你班友又話有問題，堆mk 5p仔當年都係噉打，喺高登嗰陣你地又話要正字又盛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日肥絲提下你正字，咗、蘺、唔使等等等等都係一樣，「係、系」分別都係個企人邊，點解打其他字你地唔肯打番邊旁，而「係」、「系」就捉得咁緊？「吾」都係少左個口字邊炸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦你地剩係話人好撚煩破壞討論氣氛，但試問5p仔有point嗰陣你地點對待人？成班接龍負皮上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解今日就由得自己打錯？<br />\n<br />\n我自問都唔知自己打錯噉多字，但起碼我知道自己錯嘅時候會改，唔係成堆小學雞開post批鬥+投票話ban佢。唔符合大眾意見就ban。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地究竟係真正支持正字，定係覺得同自己習慣唔同就屌人用個「系」、「吾」字？</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：自己都改緊，「喺」、「係」想知用法係點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cddd06802bd422a01a08e20afbf20b7a4f1ff01","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23faed3b95403293a51483eb6676b7515f1eac75","tid":573262,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"咁你點睇佢啲「右」？"},{"pid":"e095c4b04f46484047eb49da1a09c0f5412e6d94","tid":573262,"uid":21423,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19b607b6d64c098a273bcf50fe3bf3b746e04b15","tid":573262,"uid":76993,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e095c4b04f46484047eb49da1a09c0f5412e6d94","tid":573262,"uid":21423,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"右你老母"},{"pid":"b5ea4cc916c6d43c7d3da7e27aa7622e2b46ee17","tid":573262,"uid":19028,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"支持肥絲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575c72884e567adfe6205cc42bdf3e0aee3b3b29","tid":573262,"uid":55736,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔正正常常就已經唔係連登仔啦<br />\n<br />\n以前高登起碼仲有堆專業人士有識之士，<br />\n<br />\n依家呢？<br />\n<br />\n得翻正常人同傻仔炸！<br />\n<br />\n連登本身自己已經係花生。"},{"pid":"4d58371dcb7b877012eb2abfb67b1f8aa225e07e","tid":573262,"uid":114798,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔覺寫系字有問題<br />\n唔影響討論既話寫錯一兩隻字有乜問題啊<br />\n咪咁小學雞啦好心<br />\n咁中意捉錯字<br />\n你係咪一隻錯字都完全唔會錯先？"},{"pid":"2c65fb4cd155259437bb7d864007869553d1e8fb","tid":573262,"uid":109780,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"係=是 e.g. 我係你老豆<br />\n喺=在 e.g. 我喺你屋企<br />\n兩者意思不同讀音亦不同<br />\n<br />\nbtw肥絲你幼稚園畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214f858b17ca86bf671abdadff9ee627788bf1d7","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"23faed3b95403293a51483eb6676b7515f1eac75","tid":573262,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"咁你點睇佢啲「右」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"系你老母、吾你老母同「唔見埋右」有咩分別？<br />\n出發點都係屌打錯字嗰條友，只係佢嘅講法令你覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但實際上你打左嘅時候有冇諗起肥絲嘅煩膠提你打「咗」？如果有，好似出面成堆垃圾玩批鬥噉，其實肥絲已經算成功。<br />\n起碼我提堆學生寫正字都無噉成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f606e484e88e0df8997faec80d6aa5ec4db77786","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d58371dcb7b877012eb2abfb67b1f8aa225e07e","tid":573262,"uid":114798,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔覺寫系字有問題<br />\n唔影響討論既話寫錯一兩隻字有乜問題啊<br />\n咪咁小學雞啦好心<br />\n咁中意捉錯字<br />\n你係咪一隻錯字都完全唔會錯先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"系你老母，我唔同意唔影響討論，其實字嘅演變對文化影響極大，錯字可以影響十幾年嘅文化研究。<br />\n當初嘅俗字只係求方便，如隸書，但今時今日追求更高層次嘅文化，唔理錯字只係文化上嘅倒退。"},{"pid":"c9f41b2b30aa8b719579fbd1adbc7f94d700492e","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c65fb4cd155259437bb7d864007869553d1e8fb","tid":573262,"uid":109780,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"係=是 e.g. 我係你老豆<br />\n喺=在 e.g. 我喺你屋企<br />\n兩者意思不同讀音亦不同<br />\n<br />\nbtw肥絲你幼稚園畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"同意你嘅用法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bc7939e7e8f25648a62ef94fd07fbdf60fd9e2","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e095c4b04f46484047eb49da1a09c0f5412e6d94","tid":573262,"uid":21423,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"萬幾人嘅正評令我感受到當年係前線聽到後面唱今天我既感覺。"},{"pid":"f9d99aa74b8eaf34dd01d3f3cac6d0a946910302","tid":573262,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"舊登放寬左同既係因為當年速成<br />\n咗同嘅都係好後<br />\n所以容許打左 既<br />\n企唔係咁呀都係頭兩頁<br />\n所以先見親都屌<br />\n明無？"},{"pid":"8c0df6cc3c23e98a845ef5f93ec33f1ce3f06ba3","tid":573262,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"系字係公認5p字，明明反5p字，唔係佢寫啱定寫錯，係反5p文化同埋趕走5p仔，偷換概念失敗"},{"pid":"94d9f4045748d75379c16c24038da38c22cf975d","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d99aa74b8eaf34dd01d3f3cac6d0a946910302","tid":573262,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"舊登放寬左同既係因為當年速成<br />\n咗同嘅都係好後<br />\n所以容許打左 既<br />\n企唔係咁呀都係頭兩頁<br />\n所以先見親都屌<br />\n明無？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"明白，所以我嗰陣都同意噉嘅睇法。<br />\n但今時今日已經可以完全解決唔方便嘅問題，點解連登仔仲要企硬撐錯字？要以劣幣驅逐良幣？"},{"pid":"3ff91c545dff6b19433d410f4d963467c6600ef9","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c0df6cc3c23e98a845ef5f93ec33f1ce3f06ba3","tid":573262,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"系字係公認5p字，明明反5p字，唔係佢寫啱定寫錯，係反5p文化同埋趕走5p仔，偷換概念失敗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"唔同意，一我同你睇法唔同，所以無偷換概念嘅邏輯問題。<br />\n08定09年個陣攻擊5p，大家確實係為左反5p嘅mk文化，但當時學術台已經有提到用依堆字係懶同歪音嘅問題，吾系甘牙，「甘」、「牙」同「咁」、「啊」係唔同音，因此當時唔只係反5p文化，仲係帶頭捍衛正字正音。<br />\n<br />\n如果連登仔係求方便死撐錯字，你地同毛魔撐簡體字有咩分別？簡體字仲有文化過你地堆錯字，人地起碼有參考小篆、隸書。定係你地係反虫蟈文化而唔係反字體問題？噉毛係真正嘅偷換概念搬龍門。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e60546c1a8aca788f4669f7b2e7d810ef48219","tid":573262,"uid":294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e095c4b04f46484047eb49da1a09c0f5412e6d94","tid":573262,"uid":21423,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"5f5aa0dc6d87458d8e2a633b2f8ddb5fbe380083","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"連自己用開嘅文字都唔寫好，點解人地唔淘汰依堆垃圾？還掂都係錯嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbe25065bd842eb53524a628189231b11e23bdc","tid":573262,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e60546c1a8aca788f4669f7b2e7d810ef48219","tid":573262,"uid":294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e095c4b04f46484047eb49da1a09c0f5412e6d94","tid":573262,"uid":21423,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"講得好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddb155c50c1a2cf3da34bb8fa962bb41b2f0b61","tid":573262,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"其實好多連登仔都潛移默化噉打正字/一直打開正字，只係有堆固執+懶到仆街嘅垃圾唔想改。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d21d3a5335f7caf2ecfe25df54700cee35bee84","tid":573262,"uid":170946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"同感，連登d正字L真係巧L煩<br />\n得啦巧你老母丫嘛，明架啦禾走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49859c36e728e7587c7765603e447f36e14f488","tid":573262,"uid":23815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"已經有念頭返高登個死城<br />\n堅守左咁耐既反5p都可以有班小學雞搏上位challenge <br />\n反5p文化 = 反sms字入侵時代既事<br />\n高登同連登難聽啲講係不能分割 <br />\n您唔like既麻煩您躝返出去5p揾同聲同氣既人<br />\n呢到多您班小學雞唔多 少您一個唔少<br />\n呢句說話係我身上亦一樣 只不過係想睇下客家佔地主可以去到咩地步 <br />\n<br />\n望撚住啲小學雞私怨借刀 吾系甘牙充斥每個post 之後仲要大大聲話唔關您事既咪唔好留名 真係心諗您班毛都未撚生齊既當自己係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ec8bb1c603bc31c12dc67aaf395377d1717bbc","tid":573262